reviewText: Venus Versus Virus Vol. 2-EpidemicThis volume is the 2nd installement in the Venus versus Virus anime serie and is the best of the three, Lucia and Sumire are still chasing demons but this time, new caracters make their apparence and add a lot to the basic plot. We know more about Lucia & Sumire powers and make you whant for more. Venus is a good serie, but I can understand that it might not be like by everybody.
